data.description: This lovely 3 Bedroom, 2 and a half bath Country Cottage with 2145 Square Ft of Open Concept Living on a 6.69 acre tract of land that has a 2 acre lawn surrounded by natural forest. This cottage has been fully updated while retaining many aspects of the original country home. With soaring ceilings, a spacious kitchen with an abundance of cabinetry and the adjacent dining room filled with natural light, this home is ready for family and friends to enjoy! The Master Suite is spacious that features a large walk-in closet and a bath filled with natural light. Outside is a large back porch that overlooks the beautiful lawn and surrounding forest. This home is warm and inviting. Just a 20 minute drive to I-10, shopping and dining, and close to Hwy190, You can enjoy country living and still be close to everything else! Please call for your private showing today!  All measurements are more or less.
